c0000000
00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:09.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing deeply]</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:12.890 --> 00:00:14.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:19.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Morning.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:19.190 --> 00:00:20.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Good morning to you, too, Mai.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:21.310 --> 00:00:22.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did you not sleep?</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:23.070 --> 00:00:25.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- To be honest with you,
not even a wink.</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:25.190 --> 00:00:27.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're not trying to blame me,
are you?</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:27.490 --> 00:00:29.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How can you sleep
so soundly like that?</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:29.660 --> 00:00:31.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Especially when sharing a bed.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:31.570 --> 00:00:33.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I've been going
to various places</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:33.490 --> 00:00:35.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for filming since I was small.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:35.240 --> 00:00:37.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, sleeping next
to you doesn't really</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:37.620 --> 00:00:38.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>change anything for me.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:41.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, that's a relief to hear.
In that case,</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:41.540 --> 00:00:43.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll have to pull some pranks
on you the next time we do this.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't think you even have
the guts to do that.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:47.630 --> 00:00:50.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're going to Fujisawa and then
to school from noon, right?</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:51.130 --> 00:00:53.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go step outside so
I can start getting ready.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:57.390 --> 00:00:59.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's the next morning
but like before,</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:59.980 --> 00:01:02.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai isn't visible
to anyone else but me.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:01:05.980 --> 00:01:06.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000021
00:01:09.650 --> 00:01:12.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000022
00:01:12.660 --> 00:01:15.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[The Peggies' "Kimi no sei"]</b></Default>

c0000023
00:01:15.620 --> 00:01:22.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000024
00:01:57.910 --> 00:02:04.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:24.230 --> 00:02:31.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:39.160 --> 00:02:40.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:40.410 --> 00:02:41.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's he up to?</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:41.410 --> 00:02:42.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It was so funny.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And when I asked him about
it yesterday,</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:44.830 --> 00:02:46.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he said he was totally fine.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:46.080 --> 00:02:47.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's exactly like
it always is, right?</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:50.090 --> 00:02:52.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are they ignoring you more
than they usually do,</b></Default>

c0000034
00:02:52.670 --> 00:02:54.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or are you really invisible?</b></Default>

c0000035
00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:55.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll check my classroom.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:02:58.430 --> 00:02:59.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa.
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:00.390 --> 00:03:01.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have some bad news.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:02.310 --> 00:03:04.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks like everyone other
than the two of us</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:04.430 --> 00:03:06.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>have forgotten about Sakurajima.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:06.600 --> 00:03:09.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least, Kunimi didn't remember
when I asked him.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:09.150 --> 00:03:10.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wait, he didn't?</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:10.520 --> 00:03:11.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- For real?
No way!</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:11.980 --> 00:03:13.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You.
- Oh.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:13.780 --> 00:03:16.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, you know who Sakurajima
is, right?</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:16.820 --> 00:03:18.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, Sakura?</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:18.370 --> 00:03:20.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mai Sakurajima,
one of the third-years.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:20.620 --> 00:03:22.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hold on. Tomoe.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:22.290 --> 00:03:24.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why is the guy from
the rumors talking to you?</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:24.450 --> 00:03:26.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, I really don't know.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:26.370 --> 00:03:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- None of us know who
you're talking about.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:27.830 --> 00:03:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We should go.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:30.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How could you
have forgotten her?</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:30.630 --> 00:03:32.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't just forget
a celebrity!</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:33.130 --> 00:03:34.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey. Hey!</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:36.550 --> 00:03:38.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There is one possibility I
can think of.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:38.590 --> 00:03:39.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:39.850 --> 00:03:41.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did you fall asleep
last night?</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:41.390 --> 00:03:43.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, I wasn't able to.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:43.270 --> 00:03:45.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I actually had
the same problem.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:03:45.180 --> 00:03:46.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000061
00:03:46.940 --> 00:03:48.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> - It's nothing more than a gues
for now,</b></Default>

c0000062
00:03:49.020 --> 00:03:50.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I think that could be
the reason.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:03:50.690 --> 00:03:53.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're saying it's because
we didn't sleep?</b></Default>

c0000064
00:03:53.980 --> 00:03:56.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You remember the talk we
had about measurement theory?</b></Default>

c0000065
00:03:57.200 --> 00:03:59.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Schrodinger's Cat, right?</b></Default>

c0000066
00:03:59.490 --> 00:04:01.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- To be honest,
I thought it was ridiculous,</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:01.660 --> 00:04:04.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but witnessing it in real time
brings a chill to my spine.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:04.580 --> 00:04:07.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You mean puberty syndrome?
- No.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:08.330 --> 00:04:10.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm specifically referring
to the fact that she</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:10.380 --> 00:04:12.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was treated like
the atmosphere even before</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:12.710 --> 00:04:14.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>her puberty syndrome started.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:16.050 --> 00:04:19.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> Everyone at school unconsciousy
ignored Sakurajima.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:19.300 --> 00:04:21.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even I took the hints
 and didn't think anything about</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:21.510 --> 00:04:23.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the situation despite
it being strange.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:24.310 --> 00:04:25.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, if you don't
question it,</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:26.060 --> 00:04:27.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's easy to fall into.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:27.890 --> 00:04:30.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's exactly why I think
our biggest clue lies in</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:32.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the atmosphere within
this school.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:33.020 --> 00:04:35.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She isn't observed by any
of the students or faculty</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:36.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in this place,</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:36.740 --> 00:04:39.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so her existence
hasn't been confirmed.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:42.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Basically, this school is like
a box for Sakurajima</b></Default>

c0000083
00:04:42.740 --> 00:04:44.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she's the cat inside.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:04:45.740 --> 00:04:48.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If recognition and observation
are the keys,</b></Default>

c0000085
00:04:48.500 --> 00:04:51.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then sleep is the catalyst
for the memory loss because</b></Default>

c0000086
00:04:51.420 --> 00:04:53.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's when the human
consciousness is inactive.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:04:54.170 --> 00:04:55.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That logic makes sense to me.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:57.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wait, so that means...</b></Default>

c0000089
00:04:58.840 --> 00:05:00.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:00.970 --> 00:05:04.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If I'd slept
then right now I'd also...</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:07.390 --> 00:05:08.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:08.930 --> 00:05:09.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is something wrong?</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:09.850 --> 00:05:10.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, no.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:10.980 --> 00:05:12.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't you have work today?</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:13.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, but--</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:13.810 --> 00:05:15.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You have to keep on top
of that stuff.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:15.940 --> 00:05:17.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I promise you I'll be fine.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:17.820 --> 00:05:19.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right, see you tomorrow!</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:22.360 --> 00:05:23.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nobody is looking at her.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:25.370 --> 00:05:27.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai isn't being observed
by anyone.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:28.040 --> 00:05:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which makes
her existence unconfirmed.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:30.580 --> 00:05:32.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So she's disappearing.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:35.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because if no one
recognizes you...</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:35.790 --> 00:05:38.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the same as not existing
in this world.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:39.090 --> 00:05:40.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:40.760 --> 00:05:42.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're saying that school
is where this all started,</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:43.050 --> 00:05:44.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why are people who have
no connections</b></Default>

c0000108
00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:46.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to this place suddenly unable
to see her, too?</b></Default>

c0000109
00:05:46.970 --> 00:05:50.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I guess it's entirely possible
that Sakurajima somehow carried</b></Default>

c0000110
00:05:50.430 --> 00:05:52.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the atmosphere outside of here.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:05:52.310 --> 00:05:53.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And even if she didn't,</b></Default>

c0000112
00:05:53.770 --> 00:05:56.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>atmospheres can easily spread
on their own.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:05:56.770 --> 00:05:59.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These days everyone reads
it without question.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:00.190 --> 00:06:02.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- An atmosphere's invisible,</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:05.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it does in fact exist
around us.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:05.370 --> 00:06:07.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not something that's wise
to fight against.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:12.040 --> 00:06:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- While you're sleeping,</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:13.580 --> 00:06:15.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's not possible to
 be conscious of another person.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:16.670 --> 00:06:18.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So right when you
lose consciousness,</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:18.630 --> 00:06:21.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the atmospherization phenomenon
takes over.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:22.670 --> 00:06:24.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If I sleep,
I'll forget.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:25.890 --> 00:06:27.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]
- [gulping]</b></Default>

c0000123
00:06:27.220 --> 00:06:29.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother, what
is that you're drinking?</b></Default>

c0000124
00:06:30.020 --> 00:06:32.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
Midterms start tomorrow.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:32.310 --> 00:06:34.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's to help me stay focused.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:34.520 --> 00:06:36.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, isn't it your bedtime?</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:38.060 --> 00:06:40.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gotta do this while I'm still
conscious enough to do so.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:45.860 --> 00:06:46.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales deeply]</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:47.530 --> 00:06:48.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:54.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is written hereafter,
to be honest,</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:57.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is something you might find
completely unbelievable.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:57.630 --> 00:06:59.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But everything
is true so make sure</b></Default>

c0000133
00:06:59.630 --> 00:07:01.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to read it till the very end.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:01.840 --> 00:07:02.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have to.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:12.390 --> 00:07:14.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your face looks
so disheveled.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:15.190 --> 00:07:17.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And you're looking
as beautiful as ever today.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:20.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
Your tie is even crooked.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:20.940 --> 00:07:22.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not that I'm complaining,</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:22.320 --> 00:07:23.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I really didn't think
we'd be pretending</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:23.990 --> 00:07:25.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be newlyweds this early on.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:25.700 --> 00:07:28.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't be as stupid
as your face looks.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:07:28.990 --> 00:07:31.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you also taking
the exams, Mai?</b></Default>

c0000143
00:07:31.530 --> 00:07:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bet you can cheat as much
as you want.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:07:33.830 --> 00:07:35.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't have to resort
to cheating to do well,</b></Default>

c0000145
00:07:35.710 --> 00:07:37.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>thank you very much.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:39.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although, not like it matters
since no one's going</b></Default>

c0000147
00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:41.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to hand me an exam sheet.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:07:41.880 --> 00:07:43.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You must be dedicated
if you're still going</b></Default>

c0000149
00:07:43.760 --> 00:07:45.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to school regardless.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:07:45.590 --> 00:07:48.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Even if I stay home,
I won't have anything to do.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:51.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's always possible
that maybe someone other</b></Default>

c0000152
00:07:51.810 --> 00:07:53.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than you will be able
to see me again today.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:07:53.930 --> 00:07:54.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:00.150 --> 00:08:03.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:03.570 --> 00:08:06.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, don't sleep.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:06.530 --> 00:08:08.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you sleep,
you'll forget.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:09.030 --> 00:08:10.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't sleep!</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:13.160 --> 00:08:14.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:14.450 --> 00:08:15.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:15.870 --> 00:08:18.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are those dark circles
from cramming for exams?</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:19.540 --> 00:08:20.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Futaba.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:21.290 --> 00:08:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?
