<Default><b>- [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000492
00:23:05.550 --> 00:23:08.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, do you think it's safe
to say that your hypothesis</b></Default>

c0000493
00:23:08.510 --> 00:23:09.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was correct in the end?</b></Default>

c0000494
00:23:09.720 --> 00:23:11.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Who knows?</b></Default>

c0000495
00:23:11.270 --> 00:23:13.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Illusions shown
by unstable psyches</b></Default>

c0000496
00:23:13.520 --> 00:23:16.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or strong preconceptions
of adolescence--</b></Default>

c0000497
00:23:16.190 --> 00:23:18.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if that's what puberty syndrome
really is,</b></Default>

c0000498
00:23:18.360 --> 00:23:20.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then scientific verification
won't be that reliable.</b></Default>

c0000499
00:23:22.190 --> 00:23:24.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, there's always
the possibility</b></Default>

c0000500
00:23:24.570 --> 00:23:26.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that our world is so simple,</b></Default>

c0000501
00:23:26.160 --> 00:23:28.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a single confession of love
can change it drastically.</b></Default>

c0000502
00:23:29.910 --> 00:23:32.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just like you proved today,
Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:23:32.200 --> 00:23:33.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000504
00:23:33.410 --> 00:23:34.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe you're right.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:23:37.670 --> 00:23:40.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000506
00:23:40.670 --> 00:23:43.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>["Fukashigi no Carte" plays]</b></Default>

c0000507
00:23:43.630 --> 00:23:50.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000508
00:24:29.260 --> 00:24:36.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000509
00:24:38.560 --> 00:24:42.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> - Unfortunately, Mai's situatin
 wasn't the last incident relatd</b></Default>

c0000510
00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:43.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:24:44.820 --> 00:24:46.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right after Schrodinger's Cat,</b></Default>

c0000512
00:24:47.030 --> 00:24:52.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Laplace's demon--
no, Laplace's petit devil--</b></Default>

c0000513
00:24:52.450 --> 00:24:53.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>suddenly appeared.</b></Default>

c0000514
00:24:55.660 --> 00:25:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, Sakuta.
You're such a rascal.</b></Default>

